sources.title: Love in High Gear
sources.description: Title: Love in High Gear Summary: A young couple making plans to elope are overheard by a jewel thief, who sees a chance to turn the situation to his advantage. Directed by: Frank R. Strayer Actors: Production Company: Ralph M. Like Productions Release Date: 1 May 1932 (USA) Aspect Ratio: 1.37 : 1 A young couple making plans to elope are overheard by a jewel thief, who sees a chance to turn the situation to his advantage.

sources.title: Love_in_High_Gear
sources.description: A young couple's wedding is spoiled by the theft of valuable pearls during the ceremony, and the intrigue follows them to the 'Peek Inn' where they plan to honeymoon.
